org.cloudbus.foggatewaylib.core

Interface AsyncProvider.ProgressPublisher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AsyncProvider.ProviderAsyncTask
    Enclosing class:
    AsyncProvider<T extends Data,S extends Data>

    public static interface AsyncProvider.ProgressPublisher
    Interface used for passing the progress updates from the AsyncProvider context to the AsyncProvider.ProviderAsyncTask one and finally calling Provider.publishProgresses(long, ProgressData...).
    See Also:
    AsyncProvider.ProviderAsyncTask.publish(int, String), AsyncProvider.ProviderAsyncTask.onProgressUpdate(ProgressData...), Provider.publishProgresses(long, ProgressData...)
